Photo by Calvin Harris on July 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog and body of water.

Photo shared by Calvin Harris on June 30, 2021 tagging @snoopdogg, @arianagrande, @kehlani, @lilyachty, @bigsean, @atrak, @johnlegend, @thegr8khalid, @travisscott, @future, @thuggerthugger1, @groovyq, @partynextdoor, @yrntakeoff, @pharrell, @jessiereyez, @migos, @katyperry, @nickiminaj, and @blonded. node.text: 4 years of the Funk Wav album today, I love this album, was such a mad experience getting to work with all these brilliant artists on one record, forever grateful for the opportunity
